    "He additionally studied miniatures with Samuel Lover (1797-1868).": [],
    "In 1837, Burton was elected an associate member of the Royal Hibernian Academy and a full member in 1839.": [],
    "During this time, he met the antiquarian and artist George Petrie (1789-1866), who suggested he study the history of art.": [
