    "His archives are at the National Gallery, Ireland and the National Gallery London, particularly correspondence with National Gallery curator <a href=\"/wornumr\">Ralph Nicholson Wornum</a> and at the Harry Ransom Humanities Research Center, Austin, TX, letters to <a href=\"/murrayc\">Charles Fairfax Murray</a>.": [],
